      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Bridge\n\n- explicit cross-context capability inside the current session\n- does not replace the host graph or transfer ambient authority\n- current runtime: bridge loads a node-class graph, registers its dictionary entries, and creates a local instance in the source fragment\n- use this when you want controlled reach without world-merging",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
