      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Connection vs Context\n\nThe grammar is now:\n- connection semantics: `navigate`, `expand`, `bridge`\n- context semantics: `boundary`\n\n`boundary` is not a crossing. It only names the perimeter or limit that crossings relate to.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
